thread.title: Greek leftist Syriza to take 35 pct in election - 10 pct of vote counted
thread.title_full: Greek leftist Syriza to take 35 pct in election - 10 pct of vote counted | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Greek leftist Syriza to take 35 pct in election - 10 pct of vote counted
text:
ATHENS, Sept 20 The leftist Syriza party of Alexis Tsipras has won 35.07 percent of the vote in Greece's national election, according to data on the Interior Ministry website based on 10.16 percent of votes counted.
Conservative New Democracy is on 28.65 percent, the ministry website said. (writing by John Stonestreet)
